# Game Balance and Economy — Thiên Nam Engine

> Rules for balancing the game's economy, cultivation speed, and resource flow. Every number is deliberate.

---

## Core Principle: Sustainable Progression

The economy must support long-term engagement. Too generous = no reason to play. Too stingy = frustration. The sweet spot: steady progress with meaningful choices.

---

## Currency System

### Currencies and Roles

| Currency | Role | Acquisition | Sink |
|----------|------|-----------|------|
| **Bạc (Ag)** | Daily currency | Daily, quests, combat | Travel, repair, basic items |
| **Linh Thạch (ST)** | Advancement currency | Breakthrough, alchemy, rare drops | Manuals, pills, advancement |
| **Công Huân (Mer)** | Sect currency | Sect activities | Sect shop, rank benefits |
| **Danh Vọng (Rep)** | Reputation currency | Quests, public deeds | Reputation items, faction access |
| **Thiên Đạo Ấn (HS)** | Event currency | World events, seasons | Seasonal items, exclusive titles |

### Exchange Rates

```
1 Linh Thạch = 100 Bạc
1 Linh Thạch = 10 Công Huân (within sect)
Công Huân ↔ Danh Vọng: One-way, no exchange
Thiên Đạo Ấn: Non-convertible
```

---

## Economy Health Indicators

Monitor these metrics to detect problems:

| Indicator | Healthy | Warning | Critical |
|-----------|---------|---------|----------|
| Avg Silver per active player | 1,000-10,000 | >20,000 | >100,000 |
| Ag generation per day (avg) | 500-3,000 | >10,000 | >50,000 |
| Ag sink per day (avg) | 400-2,500 | <200 | <50 |
| ST in circulation (weekly) | 50-300 | >1,000 | >5,000 |
| Thanh Tâm Đan price | 15-50 ST | 50-200 ST | >200 ST |

### Auto-Correction Triggers

```typescript
// If economy is inflationary (too much money):
if (avgPlayerSilver > 20_000) {
  dailyReward *= 0.9;           // Reduce by 10%
  questRewards *= 0.9;
  repairCosts *= 1.1;           // Increase by 10%
}

// If economy is deflationary (too little money):
if (avgPlayerSilver < 500) {
  dailyReward *= 1.2;
  questRewards *= 1.2;
  repairCosts *= 0.8;
}
```

