## Cultivation Speed Balance

### Target Progression

| Player Type | Sessions/Day | Days to Kim Đan |
|------------|-------------|-----------------|
| Casual | 1 | ~1 year |
| Active | 2 | ~6 months |
| Dedicated | 4 | ~3 months |
| Hardcore | 6 | ~2 months |

**Design target: Active player reaches Kim Đan in 3-4 months.**

### Speed Adjustments

| Situation | Adjustment |
|----------|-----------|
| Seasonal (Spring/Summer) | +15% cultivation speed |
| Winter season | -15% cultivation speed |
| U Minh region | +30% speed but +2 HD/day |
| In sect HQ | +10% speed |
| Heart demon 80+ | -30% speed |
| Severe injury | -20% speed |

### Anti-Farm Rules

| Action | Limit | Penalty |
|--------|-------|---------|
| Cultivation sessions | 6/day max | Cooldown doubles |
| Forced cultivation | 3/day max | Heart demon accumulation |
| Encounters | 5/day max | Diminishing returns |
| Alchemy attempts | 10/day max | Ingredient shortage |

