## Alchemy Balance

### Success Rates by Quality

| Pill Tier | Easy | Medium | Hard | Expert |
|----------|------|--------|------|--------|
| **Success** | 90% | 70% | 50% | 30% |
| **Thượng Phẩm** | 50% | 30% | 15% | 5% |
| **Cực Phẩm** | 10% | 5% | 2% | 0.5% |

### Đan Kiếp (Pill Tribulation)

- Triggered on Cực Phẩm creation: 5% chance
- Survival chance = 50% + (FQ / 2)
- Win: Bonus rewards + public log
- Lose: Ingredient loss + injury + HD +10

### Economy Check: Pills

| Pill | Ingredient Cost | Market Value | Profit Margin |
|------|---------------|--------------|---------------|
| Thanh Tâm Đan | 15 ST | 25-50 ST | 40-130% |
| Trúc Mạch Đan | 50 ST | 100-200 ST | 100-200% |

**Cap: Max 10 high-quality pills per player per week to prevent flooding.**

