## Sect Economy

### Treasury Guidelines

| Sect Rank | Max Treasury | Weekly Salary Cap | Tax Rate |
|-----------|------------|-----------------|---------|
| ★ | 10,000 ST | 1,000 ST | 5% |
| ★★ | 50,000 ST | 5,000 ST | 8% |
| ★★★ | 100,000 ST | 10,000 ST | 10% |
| ★★★★ | 200,000 ST | 20,000 ST | 12% |
| ★★★★★ | Unlimited | No cap | 15% |

### Sect Salary Formula

```
weeklySalary = min(
  treasury / (memberCount × 4),  // 4-week runway
  100 * sectRankMultiplier
)
```

