## Anti-Exploit Rules

### Farming Detection

| Pattern | Detection | Response |
|---------|-----------|----------|
| >4 cultivation/hour | Timestamp analysis | 4-hour cooldown |
| Infinite alchemy loop | Ingredient flow audit | 24-hour ban |
| Combat exploit | Damage variance check | Roll back, warn |
| Duplicate items | Transaction audit | Revert, ban |
| Rate limit bypass | IP + user tracking | IP block |

### Rate Limits

| Action | Limit | Window |
|--------|-------|--------|
| `/cultivate` | 6 | per day |
| `/alchemy` | 10 | per day |
| `/encounter` | 5 | per day |
| `/breakthrough` | 1 | per 24h |
| Button interactions | 30 | per minute |

---

## Balance Change Process

When adjusting balance:

1. **Document the change** — What, why, expected impact
2. **Preview on 10%** — Test on subset of players for 24-48 hours
3. **Monitor metrics** — Watch economy health indicators
4. **Full deploy** — If preview shows improvement
5. **Monitor 7 days** — Watch for unexpected effects
6. **Log in audit** — Record change with justification

**Rule: Never adjust by more than ±20% in one change. Incremental tuning only.**
